_sText:
I really enjoyed doing the map runewords so I decided to do another map with the same style. Every stage/bonus try to keep the spirit of its prequel, enjoy.

IMPORTANT FOR SERVER HOSTERS: 1st group of trigger on s4 are fucked by 64 units (spawn to first glass wall), you can strip the whole of it if you want, sorry for that

Map: tier 3-4 (depends on server), 4 stages, 6 bonuses.
b1 by not_a_zombie
b3 by kreal
b5 by wayne3288
b6 by Mr.Cow

Download link (css): http://gamebanana.com/maps/198659
Download link (csgo): http://gamebanana.com/maps/198660
